@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "FAQ";
}

<div class="container">
    <header>
        
        <img id="logo" alt="FabianMusic logo" src="~/images/MusicNotes.jpg"
        class="img-fluid rounded" />
    
    <h1 class="display-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    </header>
    <br />
    <main>
        <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" 
                    aria-controls="collapseOne">
                        1. What is the main purpose of this page?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <strong>We are committed to enhancing the music shopping experience</strong> by categorizing artists based on genre and release 
                        date, enabling users to explore and discover new musical treasures.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" 
                    aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                        2. Can I browse and purchase sheet music or digital downloads in the app?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <strong>Yes, our app offers a wide selection of sheet music and digital downloads.</strong> You can browse through various categories, such as 
                        classical, pop, jazz, and more. Once you find the sheet music or digital download you want, you can purchase it securely within the app.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" 
                    aria-controls="collapseThree">
                        3. How can I get updates on new arrivals, promotions, and discounts in the app?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        You can stay updated on new arrivals, promotions, and discounts by enabling push notifications in the app's settings. Additionally, 
                        we regularly send out newsletters and emails to our subscribers, so make sure you're subscribed to our newsletter for the latest 
                        news and offers.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false"
                            aria-controls="collapseThree">
                        4. What payment methods are accepted in the app?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        We accept a variety of payment methods, including major credit cards (Visa, MasterCard, American Express), PayPal, and Apple Pay. You can
                        choose your preferred payment method during the checkout process.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false"
                            aria-controls="collapseThree">
                        5. Is there a loyalty or rewards program for frequent customers?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        Yes, we offer a loyalty program for our frequent customers. You can earn points for each purchase you make in the app, and these 
                        points can be redeemed for discounts on future purchases. The more you shop, the more you save.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false"
                            aria-controls="collapseThree">
                        6. How can I navigate to other sections or related content from this page?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        To navigate to other sections or related content, you can use the menu or navigation bar typically located at the top or side 
                        of the page. It may contain links to different sections, categories, or related articles.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer class="border-top footer text-muted">

        &copy; 2023 - FabianMusic - <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Privacy">Privacy</a>

    </footer>
</div>
